### Stripe Checkout Fix
The Stripe SDK had connectivity issues on Vercel ("Request was retried 2 times" error).
Workaround: Use raw fetch API to Stripe's REST endpoints instead of the SDK.
See: `splice-website/src/app/api/checkout/route.ts`

